item.title: About
item.description: Work Experience 3.5+ years experience working as a data and information analyst for the Ministry of Business, Innovation and Employment. In this role I helped roll out a number of data initiatives aimed at increasing the data maturity of the NZ Companies Office. These initiatives ranged from creating a cross-registry data catalogue, undertaking data quality and governance excercises and working with stakeholders to design analytical solutions to business problems.
